WEBVTT

00:04:58.720 --> 00:05:00.016
They returned to a village,

00:05:00.040 --> 00:05:02.480
and this village woman
turned to them and said,

00:05:03.320 --> 00:05:05.480
"You will not abandon the fight.

00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:08.160
You will return to the fire,

00:05:09.960 --> 00:05:11.560
and I will lead you."

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:14.656
She mounted a horse.

00:05:14.680 --> 00:05:16.336
She donned a turban.

00:05:16.360 --> 00:05:19.176
And with sword in her hand
and fire in her eyes,

00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:21.016
she led them where no one else would.

00:05:21.040 --> 00:05:23.720
She became the one she was waiting for.

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:29.576
"Don't abandon your posts, my dear."

00:05:29.600 --> 00:05:31.656
My grandfather saw me as a warrior.